{
  "text": "In order to extract an empirical curve of oxygen concentration from the Early-Middle Pleistocene benthic foraminiferal assemblages, the equation of [CITATION_1] : y=1.686+ 0.033337x is used, where y is the oxygen concentration in ml l 1 and x is the Benthic Foraminiferal Oxygen Index (BFOI) value. The BFOI is calculated following the equations of [CITATION_2] :",
